Outdoor Lounge Area
www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/32849

Details
 When the sun is shining there's nothing like sipping ice cold drinks in comfort. This outdoor lounge area is a perfect backdrop for chatting, laughing or just chilling. Includes many props such as sofa, table, foot stool, glasses, bottle, coasters, plants, grass, decking, cushions, sculptures, glass bowls, lemons and limes, sofa throw and lighting.

There are two colour versions for the table, sofa and foot stool, white and dark grey wicker, as well as olive and mushroom cushions.

Outdoor Lounge Area Extras

Details
 Give the Outdoor Lounge Area are warm a vibrant look with this textures and props add-on. Includes new textures for walls, floors, soft furnishings, sofa, table, glassware, fruit bowl, platter and coasters. There are a number of brand new props such as wooden canopy, lanterns, lavender plants, side unit, magazine, oranges, wine bottle, wine glass, wall lights and old fashioned stable styled door.
